data.description: Looking for a newly designed condo on North Padre Island that has never been lived in? This home is just a golf cart away from the beach, local restaurants and much more. Featuring a pool in the backyard and an open concept living room! With all the bedrooms upstairs along with a laundry room this townhome makes for an amazing opportunity for anyone looking to call North Padre Island Home. The bonus to this property is that they allow short term rentals making it a great investment property or to be a home year round!
